<mvc:View controllerName="webapp.controller.pharmacy.PrescriptionMonitoring" xmlns:l="sap.ui.layout" xmlns:smartTable="sap.ui.comp.smarttable" xmlns:smartFilterBar="sap.ui.comp.smartfilterbar" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:f="sap.f" xmlns:m="sap.m" xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc" xmlns:tnt="sap.tnt" height="100%">
	<m:Page floatingFooter="true" class="sapUiContentPadding sapUiResponsivePadding--header sapUiResponsivePadding--subHeader sapUiResponsivePadding--content sapUiResponsivePadding--footer">
		<m:headerContent>
			<m:Button text="E-Rezepte Anfordern" type="Emphasized" />
			<m:Button text="Alle Medikamente bestellen" type="Ghost" />
		</m:headerContent>
		<m:customHeader>
			<m:Bar class="bar">
				<m:contentLeft>
					<m:Text text="{i18n>prescriptionControlTitle}" class="tabsTitel"></m:Text>
				</m:contentLeft>
				<m:contentMiddle></m:contentMiddle>
				<m:contentRight>
					<m:RadioButton text="Alle" selected="true"></m:RadioButton>
					<m:RadioButton text="SpÃ¤ter zu kontrollieren"></m:RadioButton>
					<m:RadioButton text="Kontrollierbar"></m:RadioButton>
					<m:RadioButton text="Nicht gescannt"></m:RadioButton>
					<m:RadioButton text="Zur Signatur mit HBA"></m:RadioButton>
				</m:contentRight>
			</m:Bar>
		</m:customHeader>
		<m:content>
			<m:FlexBox height="50px" alignItems="Center" justifyContent="SpaceBetween" class="medicamentBox">
				<m:Text text="Rezeptkontrolle" class="mediumFont" />
				<m:HBox>
					<m:Toolbar>
						<m:SearchField width="100%" placeholder="Suche" />
					</m:Toolbar>
					<m:Button icon="sap-icon://paste" type="Transparent" />
					<m:Button icon="sap-icon://filter" type="Transparent" />
					<m:Button icon="sap-icon://group-2" type="Transparent" />
					<m:Button icon="sap-icon://action-settings" type="Transparent" />
					<m:Button icon="sap-icon://print" type="Transparent" />
					<m:Button icon="sap-icon://full-screen" type="Transparent" />
				</m:HBox>
			</m:FlexBox>
			<m:Table>
				<m:columns>
					<m:Column>
						<m:Label text="Rezeptnr." />
					</m:Column>
					<m:Column>
						<m:Label text="Abgabedatum" />
					</m:Column>
					<m:Column>
						<m:Label text="Kunde" />
					</m:Column>
					<m:Column>
						<m:Label text="Gesamt" />
					</m:Column>
				</m:columns>
				<m:items></m:items>
			</m:Table>
		</m:content>
		<m:footer>
			<m:OverflowToolbar>
				<m:ToolbarSpacer/>
				<m:Button text="Jetzt dispensieren" type="Emphasized" />
			</m:OverflowToolbar>
		</m:footer>
	</m:Page>
</mvc:View>